Back Blow Air Nozzle For Cleaning Tiny Inside Diameters
EXAIR’s Model 1004SS, M4 NPT Back Blow Air Nozzle has been designed to deliver the smallest, most effective airflow for blowing debris and liquids from small pipe or hose inside diameters, channel, bores, holes, internal threads and other internal part features. 
